## 5. raw#10 honest C3

1. **risperidone Risperdal 2006** = first FDA ASD irritability 5-16세. D2 + 5-HT2A atypical antipsychotic 가 ASD core 가 아닌 irritability + aggression 부수 증상 적응증. core social-communication deficit 의 FDA approval 은 여전히 0 (2026년).
2. **aripiprazole Abilify 2009** = second FDA ASD irritability 6-17세 (cross-adolescent). D2 partial agonist + 5-HT2A. weight gain 부작용이 risperidone 보다 적은 것으로 알려짐. 그러나 metabolic side effect + tardive dyskinesia 장기 risk 동일.
3. **balovaptan Phase 2 fail 2018 (Roche RG7314)** = V1A vasopressin antagonist — ASD social-cognitive 가설 paradigm. FDA breakthrough designation 2018 이전 받았으나 V1aduct + VANILLA Phase 2 negative. quantum-VQE 의 V1A vs V2 vs OXTR selectivity 가 next-gen candidate 의 핵심.
4. **bumetanide Phase 3 fail 2021 (Servier + Neurochlore)** = NKCC1 inhibitor — Cl- chloride homeostasis hypothesis paradigm. SIGN-1/SIGN-2 Phase 3 negative. CNS-selective NKCC1 + 신장 NKCC2 분리가 next-gen.
5. **arbaclofen Phase 3 fail 2014 (Seaside Therapeutics)** + **AFQ056 mavoglurant Phase 3 fail 2014 (Roche)** = Fragile X mGluR5 + GABA-B paradigm 양대 fail. animal model → 임상 translation gap 이 ASD/FXS 임상 connectome 의 핵심 lesson.
6. **gaboxadol OV101 Phase 2/3 terminated 2020 (Ovid)** = Angelman GABA-A δ extrasynaptic — ASD-adjacent. STARS Angelman negative. δ-selective tonic inhibition 가 next-gen target.
7. **oxytocin intranasal STARS Pelphrey 2021 negative** = OXTR + ASD social-cognitive 가설 paradigm. multi-site Phase 2 N=290 large-scale negative. dose + duration + biomarker stratification 한정. 그러나 mixed evidence 있음 (smaller positive study 다수).
8. **MTT (Kang 2017+2019)** = Microbiota Transfer Therapy — open-label N=18 + 2-year follow-up. controversial — open-label + small sample + parent-rated outcome bias risk. RCT 가 필요 (cross-microbiome).
9. **ABA (Applied Behavior Analysis) non-pharm 1L** = Lovaas 1987+ paradigm. 임상 1L. 그러나 25-40 hr/wk intensity + 부담 + neurodiversity advocacy 비판 (compliance-based concern). modern naturalistic developmental behavioral interventions (NDBI) — ESDM (Early Start Denver Model) Dawson 2010+ 가 alternative.
10. **wet-lab + clinical RCT 없음** — quantum-only in-silico, ASD 임상 의미 한정. ASD 가 polygenic + multifactorial + heterogeneous (1000+ rare CNV/SNV) 라서 single-target paradigm 자체 한계.

